nonempty:
protected theorem nonempty (s : positive_compacts α) : (s : set α).nonempty :=
  s.interior_nonempty.mono interior_subset
#align nonempty nonempty
is_open:
protected theorem is_open (s : compact_opens α) : is_open (s : set α) :=
  s.is_open'
#align is_open is_open
is_compact:
protected theorem is_compact (s : compact_opens α) : is_compact (s : set α) :=
  s.is_compact'
#align is_compact is_compact
interior_nonempty:
theorem interior_nonempty (s : positive_compacts α) : (interior (s : set α)).nonempty :=
  s.interior_nonempty'
#align interior_nonempty interior_nonempty
ext:
@[ext]
protected theorem ext {s t : compact_opens α} (h : (s : set α) = t) : s = t :=
  SetLike.ext' h
#align ext ext
exists_positive_compacts_subset:
theorem _root_.exists_positive_compacts_subset [locally_compact_space α] {U : set α} (ho : is_open U)
    (hn : U.nonempty) : ∃ K : positive_compacts α, ↑K ⊆ U :=
  let ⟨x, hx⟩ := hn
  let ⟨K, hKc, hxK, hKU⟩ := exists_compact_subset ho hx
  ⟨⟨⟨K, hKc⟩, ⟨x, hxK⟩⟩, hKU⟩
#align exists_positive_compacts_subset exists_positive_compacts_subset
equiv_to_fun_val:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ≃ₜ » -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr ⁻¹' » -/
/-- The image of a compact set under a homeomorphism can also be expressed as a preimage. -/
theorem equiv_to_fun_val (f : «expr ≃ₜ » α β) (K : compacts α) : (compacts.equiv f K).1 = «expr ⁻¹' » f.symm K.1 :=
  congr_fun (image_eq_preimage_of_inverse f.left_inv f.right_inv) K.1
#align equiv_to_fun_val equiv_to_fun_val

coe_finset_sup:
@[simp]
theorem coe_finset_sup {ι : Type _} {s : Finset ι} {f : ι → compacts α} : (↑(s.sup f) : set α) = s.sup fun i => f i :=
  by
  classical
    refine' Finset.induction_on s rfl fun a s _ h => _
    simp_rw [finset.sup_insert, coe_sup, sup_eq_union]
    congr
#align coe_finset_sup coe_finset_sup
